                type="chemical">
               <term xml:id="tag10">
          Granite
          
        </term>
            </rs>, which, least<lb/>
of all exhibits this property. -<lb/>
- The water found in Cavities of<lb/>
the interior of <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">many</hi> stones, particularly<lb/>
 of <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag11"
                ref="#chemical_105"
