- The Solution of siliceous &amp; aluminous<lb/>
earth by the heated &amp; slightly alkalized<lb/>
waters of Volcanic Springs, was referred<lb/>
to in a former lecture. - <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
