        </name>
               </rs>
            </del>, <add xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">near <rs xml:id="ttag84" ref="#place_1011" type="place">
                  <name xml:id="tag84" type="place">
          Morton
        </name>
               </rs> in <rs xml:id="ttag85" ref="#place_235" type="place">
                  <name xml:id="tag85" type="place">
          Scotland
        </name>
               </rs>
            </add> which<lb/>
being formed in smaller blocks<lb/>
than usual, was in a state of<lb/>
