&amp; of air. -<lb/>
- <rs xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                xml:id="ttag86"
                ref="#chemical_105"
                type="chemical">
               <term xml:id="tag86">
          Basalt
          
        </term>
            </rs> from the form of its<lb/>
