                xml:id="ttag124"
                ref="#place_241"
                type="place">
               <name xml:id="tag124" type="place">
          Lake<lb/>of Geneva
        </name>
            </rs>, &amp; the river flows out<lb/>
perfectly limpid: &amp; of a bright blue<lb/>
green colour when seen by transmitted<lb/>
light; &amp; the beach of the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">Lake</hi>
            <lb/>
annually increases, at the <hi xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                rend="underline">place</hi> where<lb/>
            <lb/>
